confirming what the president
himself, John

19:54.126 --> 19:56.361 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Carlin, has been saying in all
this.

19:56.395 --> 20:00.232 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But, again, getting back to
