instance would be
if he thought it would interfere
with the

20:26.959 --> 20:32.564 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ability of the special counsel,
Bob Mueller,
my former boss, to conduct his
investigation.

20:32.598 --> 20:38.036 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I think it's unclear here which
of the three
buckets that it might fall into,
but any time

20:38.070 --> 20:40.005 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
he says that, that's what I'm
thinking in
my head.

20:40.038 --> 20:41.640 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
It's fallen into one of those
three areas.

20:41.673 --> 20:45.444 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: All right, let's
look now at
another exchange that was
notable.

20:45.477 --> 20:48.213 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Here's Democratic Senator Dianne
Feinstein
of California.

20:48.247 --> 20:53.785 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
