President Trump's
request to drop the criminal
investigation

20:53.819 --> 20:56.088 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
into his former National
Security Adviser
Michael Flynn.

20:56.121 --> 20:57.389 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

20:57.422 --> 20:58.857 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
DIANNE FEINSTEIN (D),
California: Now, here's
the question.

20:58.890 --> 21:00.092 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
You're big.

21:00.125 --> 21:01.693 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
You're strong.

21:01.727 --> 21:08.133 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I know the Oval Office, and I
know what happens
to people when they walk in.

21:08.166 --> 21:10.969 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
There is a certain amount of
intimidation.

21:11.003 --> 21:16.808 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But why didn't you stop and say,
Mr. President,
this is wrong, I cannot discuss
this with

21:16.842 --> 21:17.809 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
you?

21:17.843 --> 21:19.011 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JAMES COMEY: It's a great
question.

21:19.044 --> 21:21.947 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Maybe, if I were stronger, I
would have.

21:21.980 --> 21:29.855 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
