was playing
in my mind, what should my
response be?

21:38.563 --> 21:40.565 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
That's why I very carefully
chose the words.

21:40.599 --> 21:42.534 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Look, I've seen the tweet about
tapes.

21:42.567 --> 21:44.970 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Lordy, I hope there are tapes.

21:45.003 --> 21:50.909 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I remember saying, "I agree he
is a good guy,"
as a way of saying, I'm not
agreeing with

21:50.942 --> 21:52.911 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
