21:52.944 --> 21:56.181 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Again, maybe other people would
be stronger
in that circumstance.

21:56.214 --> 21:59.851 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
But that was -- that's how I
conducted myself.

21:59.885 --> 22:01.253 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
I hope I'll never have another
opportunity.

22:01.286 --> 22:03.422 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Maybe, if I did it again, I'd do
it better.

22:03.455 --> 22:07.959 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: How do you --
Carrie Cordero,
listening to that, how did he
handle that?

22:07.993 --> 22:12.331 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CARRIE CORDERO: The difficulty
is that there
really was, at least from the
way that the

22:12.364 --> 22:16.568 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
