about this.

22:19.071 --> 22:25.444 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
He had Attorney General
Sessions, who is somehow
implicated in the investigation
in some way,

22:25.477 --> 22:27.746 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
to the extent that he would have
to be recused.

22:27.779 --> 22:33.785 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
This is the president who, as
the FBI director
in his executive capacity, he
does have to

22:33.819 --> 22:38.156 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
provide him with information if
the president
asks for it.

22:38.190 --> 22:43.862 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, he was in a position, I
think, where there
was nobody else that he could
really discuss

22:43.895 --> 22:48.900 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
this with, given the lack of
confirmed leadership
positions in the Department of
Justice at

22:48.934 --> 22:55.841 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
the time, and given the fact
that he is directly
reporting to the attorney
general and ultimately

22:55.874 --> 22:57.109 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
