22:57.142 --> 22:59.244 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: George
Terwilliger, how do
you read this?

22:59.277 --> 23:03.515 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
You have the senator saying, why
didn't he
just speak up in the moment?

23:03.548 --> 23:05.117 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
GEORGE TERWILLIGER: Exactly.

23:05.150 --> 23:10.088 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And, frankly, I can't buy the
argument that
there was no one he could go to.

23:10.122 --> 23:16.695 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Dana Boente, a career assistant
United States
attorney and United States
attorney, an Obama

23:16.728 --> 23:17.696 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
appointee...

23:17.729 --> 23:19.631 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Who was then
acting...

23:19.664 --> 23:22.701 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GEORGE TERWILLIGER: ... was the
acting deputy
attorney general at the time,
and was perfectly

23:22.734 --> 23:25.170 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
available for Mr. Comey to talk
to.

23:25.203 --> 23:29.674 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Comey had served with Dana when
Dana was a
United States attorney for
several years.

23:29.708 --> 23:32.911 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
So, I don't buy that
explanation.

23:32.944 --> 23:38.850 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And it's part of a pattern of
Mr. Comey resorting
to self-help because he feels
like he's the

23:38.884 --> 23:46.758 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
lone ranger who is out there
carrying the
sword of righteousness forward.

23:46.792 --> 23:51.863 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Jim has served this country
honorably for
a very long time, but I really
think, Judy,

23:51.897 --> 23:57.536 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
he made some mistakes last July
when he usurped
the function of the Department
of Justice

23:57.569 --> 24:01.239 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
in deciding about the Hillary
Clinton e-mail
case.

24:01.273 --> 24:05.710 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
He made a major mistake at that
time in, in
essence, indicting Hillary
Clinton in the

24:05.744 --> 24:10.415 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
court of public opinion, and
everything since
then has flowed the wrong way.

24:10.449 --> 24:13.118 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: How do you see
that continuum,
John Carlin?

24:13.151 --> 24:20.992 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN CARLIN: Well, look, if
true, it's hard
to even describe how unusual it
would be for

24:21.026 --> 24:24.963 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
