for me?

24:38.276 --> 24:42.280 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And I can't -- we didn't --
there was no situation
that came even close.

24:42.314 --> 24:47.185 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
If someone from the White House
called over
to the FBI and said that they
wanted the director

24:47.219 --> 24:52.557 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
