he's described.

25:00.999 --> 25:06.705 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
If it's true, I think that that
would be a
serious moment about the
separation between

25:06.738 --> 25:11.109 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
