ability to
conduct investigations free from
political

25:11.142 --> 25:12.410 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
interference.

25:12.444 --> 25:14.546 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
That's a principle that's been
strongly shared
by both parties.

25:14.579 --> 25:17.349 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So it's important to figure out
whether that
happened.

25:17.382 --> 25:21.419 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Greg Craig, how
else could
he have handled it, or was there
another way?

25:21.453 --> 25:27.559 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GREGORY CRAIG: Well, I have to
say, it's hard
for me to blame Jim Comey, when
the president

25:27.592 --> 25:29.261 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
