president.

25:47.012 --> 25:53.585 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
So, first of all, I'm
sympathetic, and I'm
willing to be somewhat more
forgiving of Jim

25:53.618 --> 25:57.889 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
