situation, which
is unprecedented and unexpected.

25:57.923 --> 26:03.562 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And we can't --
I'm trying
to think of another moment that
we know of

26:03.595 --> 26:07.766 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
