aren't hurt.

27:22.173 --> 27:23.708 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Release the entire -- release
all the tapes.

27:23.742 --> 27:24.709 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
I'm good with it.

27:24.743 --> 27:26.144 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

27:26.177 --> 27:26.778 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JOE MANCHIN: Do you believe this
will rise
to obstruction of justice?

27:26.811 --> 27:28.513 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JAMES COMEY: I don't know.

27:28.546 --> 27:30.181 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
That's Bob Mueller's job to sort
that out.

27:30.215 --> 27:31.883 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

27:31.916 --> 27:34.152 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MARTIN HEINRICH (D), New Mexico:
