together.

27:59.611 --> 28:03.481 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And I've tried to be open and
fair and transparent
and accurate.

28:03.515 --> 28:09.120 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
A really significant fact to me
is, so why
did he kick everybody out of the
Oval Office?

28:09.154 --> 28:14.059 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Why would you kick the attorney
general, the
president, the chief of staff
out to talk

28:14.092 --> 28:17.595 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
