else?

28:17.629 --> 28:22.300 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And so that, to me, as an
investigator, is
a very significant fact.

28:22.333 --> 28:26.771 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: So, Greg Craig,
are we any
closer to knowing whether the
president in

28:26.805 --> 28:29.407 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
any way committed obstruction of
justice in
here?

28:29.441 --> 28:32.544 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
GREGORY CRAIG: I think he's on
very, very
thin ice.

28:32.577 --> 28:38.216 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
First of all, I think you have
got a credible,
plausible, believable witness in
Jim Comey.

28:38.249 --> 28:41.453 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
