49:09.546 --> 49:13.850 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
YAWA HANSEN-QUAO, Leading Ladies
Network:
Our goal as an organization is
to help women

49:13.884 --> 49:18.822 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
