meet Jonathan Atkins, a
19-year-old bodybuilder

51:08.265 --> 51:14.137 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
with down syndrome who competed
in the 2017
Body Sculpting Open.

51:14.171 --> 51:17.774 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The story was produced by
students at Granby
High School.

51:17.808 --> 51:20.544 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
The student correspondent is
Jamil Aforo (ph).

51:20.577 --> 51:24.481 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JAMIL AFORO: Professional
bodybuilders are
praised for their ability to
enhance their

51:24.514 --> 51:28.118 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
external appearance, pushing the
limits of
the human body.

51:28.151 --> 51:33.457 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But for Jonathan Atkins, the
hobby has transformed
not only his body, but his life.

51:33.490 --> 51:35.959 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The 19-year-old athlete comes to
this Virginia
Beach gym, called the Houze of
Champions,

51:35.992 --> 51:42.365 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
to work out with his trainer,
Joe Hartfelder,
every week.

51:42.399 --> 51:46.470 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Jonathan was born with Down
syndrome, a genetic
disorder that stems from an
additional chromosome.

51:46.503 --> 51:48.605 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JOE HARTFELDER, Trainer: My name
is Joe Hartfelder.

51:48.638 --> 51:50.373 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
I'm a WNBF natural pro
bodybuilder.

51:50.407 --> 51:56.746 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I met Jon over a year ago, and
through his
mother, who I have known since I
was around

51:56.780 --> 51:58.615 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
6, 7 years old.

51:58.648 --> 52:05.155 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
He always showed an interest in
lifting weights
at the house and kind of doing
his own thing.

52:05.188 --> 52:09.292 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
