reason.

52:11.428 --> 52:14.197 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And there is a lot of ego in the
industry.

52:14.231 --> 52:16.299 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
And I just don't like that.

52:16.333 --> 52:21.104 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JAMIL AFORO: After working
together for about
a year, Joe encouraged Jon to
enter a local

52:21.138 --> 52:22.339 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
bodybuilding competition.

52:22.372 --> 52:27.177 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JOE HARTFELDER: I really love
people and helping
people.

52:27.210 --> 52:32.616 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
