and looking
on different things on social
media.

52:36.253 --> 52:38.455 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
So I was just like, hey, he
could do this.

52:38.488 --> 52:44.561 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LISA DUDLEY, Mother of Jonathan
Atkins: Down
syndrome has low muscle tone, so
for him to

52:44.594 --> 52:50.300 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
