times, he knows
that he is different and that
he's -- there

53:01.244 --> 53:05.615 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
are certain things that he
cannot do, but
this is one thing that he knows
that he can

53:05.649 --> 53:09.419 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
do, that, for self-confidence, I
think it's
been awesome to him.

53:09.452 --> 53:14.558 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JAMIL AFORO: With encouragement
from his trainer,
Jon traveled to Phoebus,
Virginia, in February

53:14.591 --> 53:18.195 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
2017 to compete in the Body
Sculpting Open.

53:18.228 --> 53:21.932 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
