to compete
in a challenged division section
of the competition.

53:27.237 --> 53:33.443 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
LISA DUDLEY: When I saw him on
stage, I felt
very nervous, but I was proud.

53:33.476 --> 53:38.748 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I was proud that he actually
went out in front
of all these strangers and
hundreds of people.

53:38.782 --> 53:42.252 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And it was like he had done this
a hundred
times before.

53:42.285 --> 53:44.321 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And he didn't look the first bit
nervous.

53:44.354 --> 53:45.855 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
And he looked good.

53:45.889 --> 53:49.993 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
He looked really good up there.

53:50.026 --> 53:54.264 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
When he did his one-minute
routine, this is
