53:56.433 --> 53:58.201 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JOE HARTFELDER: Oh, it was
great.

53:58.235 --> 53:59.202 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
It was great.

53:59.236 --> 54:01.104 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
